                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Pearson</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Teheran</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-01-03"><hi rend="italic">January 3,
                                1905</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Pearson reports the payment of the equivalent of $30,000 gold
                            indemnity for the murder of Mr. Labaree.)</p>
